Usage: dehighlight [-help] [ -index <integer> | -select  | -all  | -original  | <objects>]

-help                # Prints out the command usage
<object>+            # Specifies Object Pointer List. ((any_object)+, optional)
-all                 # Specifies that all objects will be dehighlighted.
                     # (bool, optional)
-index <integer>     # Specifies that the objects with the index value provided
                     # will be dehighlighted. (int, optional, min=1, max=1024)
-original            # Highlight the object through original color.
                     # (bool, optional)
-select              # Specifies that all selected objects will be
                     # dehighlighted. (bool, optional)